description:
&lt;p&gt;The Emergency Department (ED) at Blackpool Teaching Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust has an exciting opportunity for a highly motivated and experienced ED nurse to join an established Practice Development Team. We are looking for an individual who is passionate about staff development, education, clinical support and education. The right individual will be welcomed to join our existing highly motivated team within our ED.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You need to possess excellent communication, teaching and interpersonal skills and be able to actively support our Department Coordinators and Clinical Matron in delivering a high quality development programme for staff. You will be confident and competent to lead a team and also possess a comprehensive portfolio of personal development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our department covers and provides a service to a population of approximately 450,000 residents, increased during our busy holiday seasons.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We consider the Department to be an innovative, creative and friendly environment for those nurses who wish to provide high quality patient centred care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer you,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A modern forward thinking department with dedicated paediatric facilities providing 24 hour service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent opportunities for professional development supported by our own programmes tailored to meet your needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clinical Supervision, Preceptorship and Mentorship.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In addition to the requirements on the person specification, we would expect from you:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A Registered nurse with at least 5 years post registration with previous ED experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evidence of developing a change within your area&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ALS Certificate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commitment to flexible working.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameTara HassettJob titleClinical MatronEmail addresstara.hassett@nhs.netTelephone number01253 300000 bleep 980Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dept Coordinator Patricia Bowen or Victoria Smith 01253 956704&lt;/p&gt;
